nodes.text: Docking Bay 64 was a docking bay in the Mos Ila Spaceport on Tatooine during the Cold War and Galactic War. In 3643 BBY a Bounty Hunter participating in the Great Hunt confronted the Devaronian Tyresius Lokai in the docking bay.
Docking Bay 64 appears as an area on Tatooine in the 2011 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic during the Bounty Hunter class mission.
